This topic provides an overview of how to install Pivotal Container Service (PKS).

To install PKS, you must have a vSphere or Google Cloud Platform (GCP) environment with Ops Manager v2.0 deployed. If you are installing PKS on vSphere, you can also configure integration with NSX-T and Harbor. 

Consult the following table:

